{"tid":2426234,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"撤參選宣言政綱 前成員料爭取與校方談判  中大學生會明如期履新","createTime":"2021-02-28T02:48:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T03:18:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3f34b42475bf9c1f68448a24b052b56bc698ce57","tid":2426234,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T02:48:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210228/FKT5LSEXDFHDDLL2ZMVC3BUMQA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210228%2FFKT5LSEXDFHDDLL2ZMVC3BUMQA%2F&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3i%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=7b15135f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210228%2FFKT5LSEXDFHDDLL2ZMVC3BUMQA%2F&h=09403e34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210228/FKT5LSEXDFHDDLL2ZMVC3BUMQA/</a><br />\n<br />\n撤參選宣言政綱 前成員料爭取與校方談判 <br />\n中大學生會明如期履新<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中大封殺學生會當選內閣「朔夜」，朔夜昨日在其fb專頁宣佈，正式撤回參選宣言及政綱等有關文件，並將fb專頁過往發表的帖文全部刪除。有中大學生會幹事會前成員相信，朔夜正承受前所未有的壓力，會給予無條件支持，現時撤回參選宣言及政綱，屬以退為進的做法，希望可與校方有談判及商討的空間。<br />\n<br />\n朔夜昨凌晨約2時在其fb專頁發文，宣佈「正式撤回參選宣言及政綱等有關文件」，同時刪除專頁內所有帖文。此「撤回」帖文一出，至昨晚7時已獲超過2,500個讚好、600多個留言、360多個分享，網民紛紛表示支持及尊重相關決定。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GU7yqG9k3IKnZcx5iMWWBRufL4A=/1773x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5444DJSF4FGZVFEETB3RZHWVNU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGU7yqG9k3IKnZcx5iMWWBRufL4A%3D%2F1773x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5444DJSF4FGZVFEETB3RZHWVNU.jpg&h=dc291160&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中大學生會當選內閣朔夜被指言論或違國安法，日前遭校方封殺。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n代表會指妥為當選<br />\n<br />\n有網民表示，「be water，辛苦你地（哋）了」、「理解！君子不立危牆之下！撐你」及「同行到底，保重」、「無論你地（哋）做乜，香港人都會支持你，放心去，唔使擔心」。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n候任中大學生會副會長何思珩回應。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中大學生會代表會選委會於昨午5。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n代表會指所有當選單位將如期於明日履新，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n曾任中大學生會常務幹事的區議員。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前會長︰無條件支持<br />\n<br />\n林兆彬續說，在現時政治環境下，朔夜。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中大學生會前會長蘇𠗕鋒亦指，相。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n他認同中大學生會臨時行政委員會主。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n蘇𠗕鋒慨嘆，在政治帶入校園的。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中大上周四晚發「嚴正聲明」，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YRQwNAtcr7yWTRU_wrmbfotHrmU=/3024x2179/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QVX4FNQOVZEVLBMGOBSMP5WEHI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYRQwNAtcr7yWTRU_wrmbfotHrmU%3D%2F3024x2179%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQVX4FNQOVZEVLBMGOBSMP5WEHI.jpg&h=b53c81a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79f406426aaae1a78f537b1601bf06e540374353","tid":2426234,"uid":177955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T03:18:12.000Z","msg":"。。。。。。。。。。。。。"}]}